  • Constructor Details

    • PrintingHistoryItem

      public PrintingHistoryItem(String studentId, String printerId, String documentId, String paperSize, List<Integer> pageNumbers, int numberOfCopies, boolean singleSided, LocalDateTime timeOrdered, LocalDateTime timeReceived, LocalDateTime timePrinted, boolean successful)
      Creates a new printing history item.
      Parameters:
      studentId - the ID of the student who requested the printing job
      printerId - the ID of the printer which the document was printed on
      documentId - the ID of the document which was printed
      paperSize - the size of the paper which the document was printed on
      pageNumbers - the page numbers of the document which were printed
      numberOfCopies - the number of copies of the document which were printed
      singleSided - whether the document was printed single or double sided
      timeOrdered - the time at which the printing job was requested
      timeReceived - the time at which the printing job was received by the printer
      timePrinted - the time at which the printing job was completed
      successful - whether the printing job was successful or not
